- [ ] On server/command errors: if it's a bug in this project ‚Äî fix it immediately, then resume from breakpoint; otherwise report to user; do not silently fall back to direct reads or edits in `test_data`.

Using this prompt ensures that test code in `test_data` is **read and written only** through the server via MCP Proxy, so that the development process and server behavior are tested end-to-end.
